{"word":"κύδιστος","slug":"κύδιστος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>κύδιστος</b></el> <el>(κύ¯διστος, η, ον) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Superlative'>Sup.</a> of <a href='S:κυδρός'><el>κυδρός</el></a>, formed from <a href='S:κῦδος'><el>κῦδος</el></a>, as <el>αἴσχιστος</el>, <a href='S:Superlative'>sup.</a> of <a href='S:αἰσχρός'><el>αἰσχρός</el></a>, from <a href='S:αἶσχος'><el>αἶσχος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>most glorious, most honoured, noblest</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:Comparative'>comp.</a><p/></div>"}]}